page.title: 07CRANBOURNE PRIMARY SCHOOL
page.content: {The}children of Cranbourne school come from North Ascot,Winkfield,Chavey Down, Woodside,Bracknell and Maidenhead.50 children live in North Ascot,3 children live in Bracknell,1 child lives in South Ascot ,4 children live in Chavey Down,6 children live in Woodside,21 children live in Winkfield,2 children live in Warfield, 1 child lives in Windsor. {Most}children come to school by car. Some children come by bike,bus or they walk.79 children come by car,5 children come by bus,11 children ride a bike to school and 6 children walk 75 children have sandwichs, 18 children have school dinners, 9 children have snacks. {The}children of the 3rd and 4th year made all the entries for the Domesday project.
